This should be set if the GitHub Enterprise server is hosted on-premises and not reachable by public internet. If this field is left empty, no network peering will occur and calls to the GitHub Enterprise server will be made over the public internet. Must be in the format `projects/{project}/global/networks/{network}`, where {project} is a project number or id and {network} is the name of a VPC network in the project.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-"
